Package org.apache.juneau.dto.html5

Class HtmlElementContainer

java.lang.Object
org.apache.juneau.dto.html5.HtmlElement
org.apache.juneau.dto.html5.HtmlElementContainer
Direct Known Subclasses:
Audio, Canvas, Colgroup, Datalist, Dl, Figure, Head, Html, Main, Map, Ol, Optgroup, Select, Table, Tbody, Tfoot, Thead, Tr, Ul, Video
public class HtmlElementContainer extends HtmlElement
A subclass of HTML elements that contain only other elements, not text.

    • getChild

      public Object getChild(int... index)
      Returns the child node at the specified address.

      Indexes are zero-indexed.

      For example, calling getChild(1,2,3); will return the 4th child of the 3rd child of the 2nd child.

      Parameters:
      index - The child indexes.
      Returns:
      The child node, or null if it doesn't point to a valid child.

    • getChild

      public <T> T getChild(Class<T> type, int index)
      Returns the child node at the specified index.
      Type Parameters:
      T - The class type of the node.
      Parameters:
      type - The class type of the node.
      index - The index of the node in the list of children.
      Returns:
      The child node, or null if it doesn't exist.
      Throws:
      InvalidDataConversionException - If node is not the expected type.
